ge.png\" title=\"image.png\" style=\"visibility: visible; border: none; box-shadow: none; width: 722px; height: 488px;\"></span></p><p class=\"\" data-lake-id=\"5d467c2ccbba44cb4131824a43357e5e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"></p><p class=\"\" data-lake-id=\"672dcde081926b504c3ace13a5e14902\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"cdc8a98a7d716cd391e9cd0add3bd105\" id=\"jkuss\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px;\">3.再重启虚拟机，灰色字即点亮。</h3><p class=\"\" data-lake-id=\"556eced4803c2b42425a3017dd64965b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p class=\"\" data-lake-id=\"4ed1282fcaa8450e942fef8102ec62c6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span>若设置后依然不行，将可移除设备中的软盘删除，重启试一下。</span></p></div>",
